d a full library of MCP integrations — all accessible from any device on your network. Run it on your Mac, Windows, or Linux machine, then pair your phone to control everything remotely."},"7":{"id":"/docs-5","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs","content":"Think of it as your entire dev environment in one app: terminals, editors, AI assistants, and tool integrations, unified under a single interface that works across all your devices."},"8":{"id":"/docs-6","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs#quick-links","content":"Download and install Mate on macOS, Windows, or Linux."},"9":{"id":"/docs-7","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs#quick-links","content":"Open your first terminal and learn the basics."},"10":{"id":"/docs-8","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs#quick-links","content":"Chat with Claude Code, Codex, or Copilot directly in Mate."},"11":{"id":"/docs-9","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs#quick-links","content":"Connect to GitHub, Slack, databases, and many more tools."},"12":{"id":"/docs-10","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs#what-can-you-do-with-mate","content":"**Run terminals** with full PTY support, tabs, and scrollback — locally or on a paired remote device"},"13":{"id":"/docs-11","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs#what-can-you-do-with-mate","content":"**Chat with AI agents** like Claude Code, Codex, and Copilot, with tool use, conversation forking, and streaming responses"},"14":{"id":"/docs-12","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs#what-can-you-do-with-mate","content":"**Edit code** in a built-in IDE with syntax highlighting for 100+ languages, a file tree, and git integration"},"15":{"id":"/docs-13","page_id":"/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs#what-can-you-do-with-mate","content":"**Preview web apps** running on any paired device's localhost through a built-in reverse proxy"},"16":{"id":"/docs-